T1  - Wealth Distribution, Inflation Tax, and Societal Benefits of Illiquid Bonds
AU  - KIM, YOUNG SIK
AU  - LEE, MANJONG
Y1  - 2009/08/01
PY  - 2009
DA  - 2009/08/01
